## APPLICATION ARCHITECTURE

### Pages & Routes

```
/                           → Landing page (unauthenticated) / Global Feed (authenticated)
/auth/login                 → Email magic link login
/auth/callback              → Supabase auth callback
/onboarding                 → First-time user flow (2 steps)
/feed                       → Global feed (default home)
/ask                        → Post a new question
/question/[id]              → Question detail + responses
/question/[id]/outcome      → Close the loop / post outcome
/profile/[id]               → User profile
/groups                     → Your trust groups
/groups/create              → Create a new trust group
/groups/[id]                → Trust group feed + members
/groups/[id]/invite         → Invite someone to trust group
/notifications              → Notification center
/settings                   → Account settings, notification email
```

