## FLOW 1: ONBOARDING (First-Time User)

### Entry Points
- User clicks invite link from email (arrives with referrer context)
- User discovers platform organically (no invite required for global access)

### Step 1: Identity Setup + Platform Motivation

**Screen layout:** Clean, centered single-column card on white/off-white background. No sidebar, no navigation, no distractions.

**Top section — Platform Motivation:**
Large, warm heading:
> **"In a world with a billion opinions, filter the ones that matter."**

Below it, 2-3 lines of body text:
> Vouch is where real questions meet real experience. Ask what matters. Hear from people who've been there. Build circles of people you actually trust.

**Form section:**

**Field 1: Display Name**
- Label: "Your name"
- Subtext beneath the field: *"We encourage using your real name — it builds trust and helps others know who they're hearing from."*
