### Email Notifications

Sent to the user's notification_email. One email per event, not batched (for MVP). Clean, text-forward design — no heavy HTML templates.

**Notification types and triggers:**

| Event | In-App | Email | Text |
|-------|--------|-------|------|
| Someone responds to your question | ✅ | ✅ | "[Name] shared their experience on your question: [title preview]" |
| Your response rated helpful | ✅ | ✅ (batched: "X people found your experience helpful today") | "[Name] found your experience helpful" — individual in-app, batched daily via email to avoid notification spam |
