## VEILED QUESTION MECHANICS

### Posting
1. User selects "Veiled" visibility
2. Question appears in global feed with generic avatar and "A verified member" attribution
3. author_id stored in DB but omitted from API responses when is_veiled = true

### Responding
- Responders use their real identity
- Question author sees all responder identities

### Reveal Mechanic
- On question detail (author view), each response has "Reveal yourself to [Name]" button
- One-way reveal: author → specific responder only
- Notification sent to responder: "The person who asked about [title] wants to connect — it was [Name]"

### Privacy
- Veiled questions do NOT appear on author's profile
- Veiled status cannot be changed after posting

