## INVITATION SYSTEM (Updated)

### Two Entry Paths

**Path 1: Organic signup.** Anyone can create an account and access the global feed. No invite required. This enables growth beyond invite chains.

**Path 2: Trust group invite.** Existing users invite others into specific trust groups. The invite email includes the inviter's name, the group name, and why they were invited. If the invitee isn't on Vouch, they sign up first, then are added to the group.

### Invite Flow (Trust Group)

1. User goes to /groups/[id]/invite
2. Search for existing user OR enter email of non-user
3. Optional: "Why are you inviting [name]?" (becomes vouch_context)
4. System sends email:
   > **[Name] invited you to "[Group Name]" on Vouch**
   > They said: "[vouch context]"
   > Vouch is where real questions meet real experience.
   > [Join and accept invite]
5. New user signs up → completes onboarding → auto-added to the trust group

